[[File:Uganda counties.png|thumb|400px|Counties of Uganda]]
The [[Districts of Uganda|districts]] of [[Uganda]] are divided into 167 [[county|counties]], 1 city council, and 23 [[municipality|municipal councils]]. Counties are divided into [[Sub-counties of Uganda|sub-counties]].<ref name="Districts">[http://www.statoids.com/uug.html Districts of Uganda, ''Statoids'', accessed 3 August 2015]</ref> The counties are listed below, by district:<ref>[http://www.statoids.com/yug.html Counties of Uganda, ''Statoids'', accessed 3 August 2015]</ref><ref name="Districts"/>

